# Projet Darkom - Data Pipeline

## Architecture
CSV → Staging → Clean → Warehouse → Power BI

## Structure
- data/          : fichier CSV source
- scripts/       : load_staging.py, clean.py
- sql/           : staging.sql
- warehouse/     : warehouse.sql, load_wearhouse.py
- validation/    : checks.sql

## Installation
pip install -r requirements.txt

## Exécution
1. python scripts/load_staging.py
2. python scripts/clean.py
3. python warehouse/load_wearhouse.py